            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Sneltoetsen",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>\u200b<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/f59da74c728852a89b29cf5ecb6a565433663839.jpg\" class=\"height-142-pixels width-200-pixels float-right\"/>\u200b&#13; <audio controls=\"controls\" id=\"audio2018018112056\"><source src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/c/cc5e6efaca99b3cf4b6777ce912f44d3272ec8bd.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\"/></audio></p>\n<p>Als je sneltoetsen gebruikt dan kun je SNELLER werken.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" class=\"width-500-pixels\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Schermlezen aan/uit</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Control + F12</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Lezen</strong></td>\n<td><strong>F2</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Herhalen</strong></td>\n<td><strong>F6</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Pauzeren</strong></td>\n<td><strong>F3</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Stoppen</strong></td>\n<td><strong>F4</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n"
                }
            ],
